               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480821-name-1579" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1579" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1579" type="surname" value="ELLIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1579" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ELLIS</persName>
                  </hi>. On 6th Aug., about half-past six o'clock in the evening, I was in Battersea-fields—I felt a tug at my pocket, turned, and saw the prisoners close behind me—Mortimore was the closest to me—I missed my handkerchief, which I had seen safe a quarter of an hour before—the prisoners were taken—my handkerchief was found on Lucken—this is it.</p>
